<li>The contest is subject to all applicable federal, state, and local laws and regulations, and the contest or
any offers herein is void where prohibited or restricted by law.  </li>
</ul>
<p>Each monthly contest will end on the last day of the month at 11:59 PM, Eastern Standard Time.
    One eligible player with the highest rank will be awarded US $1000. </p>

<p><strong>To Enter</p></strong>

<p><strong>Existing GotChosen members </strong>simply need to Login, and click the “Apply” button for each Round on
“My Scholarship Panel” for the Evolution Games Scholarship.</p>
<p><strong>New visitors</strong> to GotChosen must complete an online registration and then click on the “Apply” button
